name: bad piece of bread but on tezos
description: nothing special, it's just a piece of bread. even worse, it's an end piece. the end of a loaf of bread should be inherently worthless. you should disregard this nft and not buy it. if you feel inclined to do so, please remember that the blockchain is permanent, and you'll forever be the man who bought the bad piece of bread. you wouldn't do that, would you, anon?
